# Map Modification Rules

## ‚≠ê THE ONLY FILE TO MODIFY

**`app/config/slidesConfig.tsx`** - This is the ONLY file you need to modify for all map changes.

When user asks to modify the map:
1. Open `app/config/slidesConfig.tsx`
2. Find the relevant slide by `id` or `title`
3. Modify camera, layers, legend, or sidePanel
4. Keep structure intact
5. **DO NOT** touch any other files

