## Slide Structure

Each slide in `malaysiaSlides.tsx` has:

```tsx
{
  id: 'unique-slide-id',
  title: 'Slide Title',
  description: 'Description',
  duration: 8000,
  camera: {
    center: [lng, lat],
    zoom: 8,
    pitch: 45,
    bearing: 0,
  },
  layers: [...],
  legend: {...},
  sidePanel: {...},
}
```

## Common Modifications

### Change Camera:
```tsx
camera: {
  center: [116.0735, 5.9804],
  zoom: 10,
  pitch: 60,
  bearing: -45,
}
```

### Change Colors:
```tsx
paint: {
  'circle-color': '#NEW_COLOR',
  'circle-radius': 8,
}
```

### Add Layer:
```tsx
layers: [
  {
    id: 'new-layer',
    source: { 
      type: 'geojson', 
      data: '/data/malaysia/category/file.geojson' 
    },
    layers: [{
      id: 'layer-id',
      type: 'circle',
      paint: { 'circle-color': '#FF5733' }
    }]
  }
]
```

### Update Legend:
```tsx
legend: {
  title: 'Legend',
  position: 'bottom-left',
  entries: [
    { label: 'Category', color: '#FF5733' },
  ],
}
```

## Remember:
- All map changes happen in `malaysiaSlides.tsx`
- Don't touch the library code
- Keep slide IDs unique
- Validate data paths exist
